# Short-lived dev WebTransport cert + private key. Regenerated by
# scripts/regen-dev-cert.sh on every `make e2e-up` / `make e2e-cert`. Cert is
# capped at 13 days because Chromium rejects `serverCertificateHashes` entries
# for any cert with more than 14 days of validity, so it would go stale in git
# anyway. The companion `localhost.cert-sha256.txt` IS tracked because it is
# regenerated atomically with the cert and is the source of truth the wasm
# client reads via `window.__VC_WT_CERT_HASHES__`.
actix-api/certs/localhost.pem
actix-api/certs/localhost.key
helm/digital-ocean-secret
helm/global/us-east/grafana/secret.yaml
helm-videocall-deployment/

