# bots-app run dir: per-participant stitched WAVs, costume y4m caches,
# captured auth/SSO storage states, AND the Phase 4 ctl-<pid>.token
# files (mode 0600; bearer token for the local HTTP control API).
# Everything under this directory is treated as sensitive / local-only.
e2e/bots-app/run/
bot/assets/costumes/

# AI
# Private, per-developer instructions for Claude in this repo. The tracked
# CLAUDE.md is shared with the whole team; CLAUDE.local.md is personal and must
# never be committed (it would otherwise be untracked-but-not-ignored, the exact
# state that gets swept into `git add -A`).
CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/agent-memory/
.claude/skills/
.claude/hooks/
